{"id":59,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":59,"title":"Chapter 54: The Promise of the Book of Mormon","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 54","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 54"],["h1","The Promise of the Book of Mormon"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_059_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p3"},"Before Moroni buried the plates for the last time, he wrote a promise to the Lamanites and to anyone else who would read the records."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.1-2"},"Moroni 10:1–2"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_059_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p5"},"He told people to read the records, really think about them, and then ask Heavenly Father if they are true."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.3-4"},"Moroni 10:3–4"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_059_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p7"},"Moroni promised that if people would ask sincerely, with faith in Christ, the Holy Ghost would help them know the records are true."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.4-5"},"Moroni 10:4–5"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_059_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p9"},"Moroni wrote that if people repent, follow Jesus Christ, and love Heavenly Father, they can become perfect."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.32"},"Moroni 10:32"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_059_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p11"},"When Moroni finished writing on the gold plates, he hid them in a stone box in the Hill Cumorah and covered the box with a big rock. His mortal work was finished."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-54-the-promise-of-the-book-of-mormon.p12"},["a.scriptu